---
title: Seitan Sloppy Joes with Arugula Salad
description: When Freida and Nate, our HelloFresh chefs, set out to create a vegetarian sloppy joe, they were determined to maintain all the flavor of the classic meat version. And guess what? They totally pulled it off. Make sure you have lots of napkins on hand for this feast—you’re going to need them!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/seitan-sloppy-joes-661da0c6.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/seitan-sloppy-joes-4e36f8a7.pdf
cuisine: North America
time required: 35 minutes
